116
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,680
to die with such a person?

117
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,390
Why?

118
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,600
Give her to me.

119
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,560
Give her to me.

120
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,040
Go away.

121
