126
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,680
I did it. So what?

127
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,430
Let me tell you something.

128
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,560
Your family didn't agree to smuggle

129
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,800
