153
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:14,960
That's right. I just want to struggle upwards.

154
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:21,550
Xiao Hongye,

155
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,030
I just want

156
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,750
